This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) category as it deals with object classification and detection using visual texture cues and shape information. The use of deep learning also suggests that it could belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) category. Additionally, the paper involves the use of web search results, which could fall under the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) category. Multimedia (cs.MM) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) are also possible categories as they are related to computer vision and machine learning.
